dct_title_s: La Pensilvania, la Nuova York, il Jersey Settentrio[na]le : con la parte occidentale del Connecticut, Massachusset-s-bay e l'Irochesia
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. In upper margin: Fogl. V. From: Storia dell' America Settentrionale del signor abate Raynal ... Venezia : Dalle stampe di Antonio Zatta, 1778. A reduced version of John Mitchell's Map of the British and French dominions in North America, 1755, containing important additions and corrections. cf. Avvertimento, p. ix, of Storia dell' America Settentrionale. Historic Maps copy 2: "Fogl. V" has been erased.
